                     <interp inst="t18470705-1598-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 6 printed books, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18470705-name-273" type="victimName">
